parse.title: List of countries by road network size

text.*:
This article needs additional citations for verification. Please help improve this article by adding citations to reliable sources. Unsourced material may be challenged and removed. (November 2016) (Learn how and when to remove this template message)

This is a list of countries by total road network size, both paved and unpaved.

Length of expressways are also included. Expressways or motorways, are the highways designed for high-speed vehicular traffic with controlled-access, free of signals, delicated right of way, without any at-grade intersections or any crossings except the terminus of a expressway.
